{"aid": "imhvax21x5w1lz", "result": {"folders": ["lecture12", "q&amp;a"], "unique_views": 56, "request_instructor_me": false, "change_log": [{"data": "imf2cyq8p802zf", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-03-30T16:25:21Z", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "type": "create"}, {"to": "imf2cyq71o52ze", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-03-31T05:38:21Z", "uid": "i0f24oie8102cr", "type": "followup"}, {"to": "imf2cyq71o52ze", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-03-31T10:49:09Z", "uid": "i0b2fq3ezjw50r", "type": "feedback"}, {"to": "imf2cyq71o52ze", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-01T12:46:51Z", "uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "type": "followup"}, {"to": "imf2cyq71o52ze", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-01T13:05:22Z", "uid": "i6w84pnmjCQ", "type": "feedback"}, {"to": "imf2cyq71o52ze", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-01T15:15:51Z", "uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "type": "feedback"}], "upvote_ids": [], "id": "imf2cyq71o52ze", "bookmarked": 7, "no_answer_followup": 2, "i_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-03-31T05:38:21Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i0f24oie8102cr", "created": "2016-03-31T05:38:21Z", "type": "followup", "no_answer": 1, "id": "imfuorg9p306no", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "This week", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 4, "data": null, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-03-31T10:49:09Z", "uid": "i0b2fq3ezjw50r", "created": "2016-03-31T10:49:09Z", "type": "feedback", "id": "img5sgb4m2142v", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "This week", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 4, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>孤儿是父亲先退出了&#xff0c;然后OS把他的 父亲pid 设置成1&#xff0c;也就是过继给第一个进程</p>\n<p>僵尸是它退出了&#xff0c;还未被回收的时候的状态。</p>"}], "subject": "<p>也就是说僵尸进程和孤儿进程是不同的&#xff1f;</p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-01T12:46:51Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "created": "2016-04-01T12:46:51Z", "type": "followup", "no_answer": 1, "id": "imhpfo40qmx476", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-01T13:05:22Z", "uid": "i6w84pnmjCQ", "created": "2016-04-01T13:05:22Z", "type": "feedback", "id": "imhq3h12p1d599", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p><tt>我的理解&#xff0c;父进程退出了子进程就会被init接管&#xff0c;这时就回收了。所以只要杀死父进程&#xff0c;子进程就不会一直是zombie。所以如果不想wait&#xff0c;有一个技巧是fork两次&#xff0c;然后删掉儿子&#xff0c;这样孙子就被init接管了&#xff08;此时该进程叫孤儿进程&#xff09;&#xff0c;执行exit就直接退出了。</tt></p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-01T15:15:51Z", "uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "created": "2016-04-01T15:15:51Z", "type": "feedback", "id": "imhur9tfmyp2h5", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>只要祖宗init没挂掉&#xff0c;它就可以定期帮助回收那些僵尸进程</p>"}], "subject": "<p>如果父进程没有执行wait, 那子进程执行exit后&#xff0c;是否会一直是“僵尸进程(zombie)”呢&#xff1f;</p>\n<p>请思考一下。</p>"}], "nr": 753, "bucket_order": 2, "config": {}, "status": "active", "tags": ["instructor-note", "lecture12", "q&amp;a"], "num_favorites": 0, "bucket_name": "Today", "q_edits": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "request_instructor": 0, "created": "2016-03-30T16:25:21Z", "is_tag_good": false, "type": "note", "s_edits": [], "my_favorite": false, "default_anonymity": "no", "t": 1459524667609, "tag_good": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "history": [{"content": "<p>更正一个今天上课时我的描述错误。上课时我对“僵尸进程”描述是不对的。抱歉&#xff0c;是我记错了。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>正确的描述是&#xff0c;子进程通过exit()退出时&#xff0c;父进程既没有结束&#xff0c;也没有通过wait()等待子进程结束&#xff0c;则子进程成为“僵尸进程(zombie)”。详细描述可参见下面链接。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>僵尸进程-百度百科</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/link?url=qgGvwXmrrXmg1OmraSy6jP89uvY_e442Rs2LFghEddn5fRn3NgoAIGFNTfwZ8CM2sGK908qrKMV3Cfb55WnJQK\">http://baike.baidu.com/link?url=qgGvwXmrrXmg1OmraSy6jP89uvY_e442Rs2LFghEddn5fRn3NgoAIGFNTfwZ8CM2sGK908qrKMV3Cfb55WnJQK</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Zombie process<br />From Wikipedia<br /><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zombie_process\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zombie_process</a></p>\n<p></p>", "anon": "no", "subject": "僵尸进程", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "created": "2016-03-30T16:25:21Z"}]}, "error": null}